To create an app called flutter_course:
flutter  create flutter_course

To open iPhone simulatore:
open -a Simulator

to open Andriod simulator:

make a connection from flutter app to Simulator :
SEA-ML-00027338:flutter_course palagiri$ pwd
/Users/palagiri/Documents/projects/flutter_course
SEA-ML-00027338:flutter_course palagiri$ flutter run

Make changes in the source code & on the terminal just hit "r" to refresh or "R" reload

Dart notes:
funcitons with one liner function defintions like:
void print_hello(){
    print("hello world");
}
cane be changed to void print_hello() => print("hello world");
